// Welcome Screen
// Name entry screen for new onboarding users and quick-resume picker for returning users.
// Stores the last-used user ID in localStorage under 'onboarding-last-user-id'.

FUNCTION WelcomeScreen()                                                EXPORT
  CALLS: listUsers (onboarding-api), createUser (onboarding-api)
  Read project and setUser, setMode from OnboardingContext.
  On mount: fetch existing users via onboardingApi.listUsers.

  selectUser(user): persist user ID to localStorage, set user and mode in context,
    navigate to /onboarding/dashboard.

  handleCreate(e): prevent default. Create a new user via onboardingApi.createUser,
    then call selectUser with the result. Show error on failure.

  Render:
    - A name input form with a "Start" button.
    - A list of existing users as clickable cards (returning user picker).
